content: Best looking icon pack ever!

This is a fresh take an the shadowed icon, each icon is a vibrant color with a contrasting white or black symbol covering it. I enjoy using this pack so much! There are tons of icons and always big updates that add more popular icons. The UI in the app (for applying the pack for several launchers, wallpapers, requesting icons etc.) is also unique and different than other icon apps UI on the market. And it's very easy to use! This is in my top 5 icon packs! Highly recommended! Great job dev!
